00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:17,090
This is an apothecary.

720
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,480
It's not a general store.

721
00:35:21,280 --> 00:35:21,980
It's not like I'm decorating the place

722
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:23,090
