723
00:35:23,400 --> 00:35:24,130
You see,

724
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,320
this is our house.

725
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:27,160
From now on, we have to stay here.

726
00:35:27,360 --> 00:35:28,880
Naturally, it shouldn't be too boring.

727
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:30,150
We have to decorate it

728
00:35:30,710 --> 00:35:31,710
with things we like.

729
00:35:33,230 --> 00:35:35,050
I think you're the only one who likes this.

730
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:40,160
How come I never knew
you liked watching fish?

731
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,990
I never knew you liked
watching birds either.

732
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,720
Everyone
has their own preferences.

733
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:50,610
You like to grind herbs, cook,

734
00:35:50,630 --> 00:35:51,630
and be a good man.

735
00:35:52,150 --> 00:35:53,150
But me?

736
00:35:53,550 --> 00:35:55,820
I like to watch birds, fish, enjoy music,

737
00:35:55,890 --> 00:35:58,260
and live my life as a shameless womanizer.

738
00:35:59,230 --> 00:36:00,230
To each his own.

